[0.002, "o", "\u001b[?25l\u001b[67;230H   \u001b[1;65r\u001b[H\u001b[M\u001b[1;67r\u001b[65;1H; this to 1 will cause PHP CGI to fix its paths to conform to the spec.  A setting\u001b[K\u001b[66;225H\u001b[0;10;7m\u000f3\u001b[65;32H\u001b[?25h"]
